{"tid":2140040,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[又係繳費處女文員]青山醫院繳費處女文員初步確診　4袁國勇曾指收錢可播毒","createTime":"2020-08-04T16:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T16:47:49.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1022db7940b8d900d210ff3dc7134c90fa12148e","tid":2140040,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:47:49.000Z","msg":"繼 4 日前，瑪麗醫院有繳費處職員確診後，今日 (5 日) 再有一名青山醫院繳費處女文員初步確診。青山醫院表示，該文員主要在醫院 D 座地下繳費處負責櫃檯收費工作，工作期間全程佩戴口罩。院方強調，收費櫃枱與公眾有膠板分隔，收費過程中職員並無與公眾有直接接觸。院方將於明日暫時關閉 D 座地下繳費處服務，期間病人可改往 C 座地下繳費處作查詢及跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/r-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E7%B9%B3%E8%B2%BB%E8%99%95%E5%A5%B3%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E9%9D%92%E5%B1%B1%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2-%E6%94%B6%E8%B2%BB%E6%AB%83%E6%9E%B1%E8%88%87%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E6%9C%89%E8%86%A0%E6%9D%BF%E5%88%86%E9%9A%94-%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E8%88%87%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E7%84%A1%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8E%A5%E8%A7%B8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2Fr-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%25B9%25B3%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2588%259D%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E6%25AB%2583%25E6%259E%25B1%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%2586%25A0%25E6%259D%25BF%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%259A%2594-%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%258E%25A5%25E8%25A7%25B8%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeagDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=df3370f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2Fr-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%25B9